OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fin self-driving cars to be 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fallowed                    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, People using self-driving cars will be 
OL,6, allowed to watch television on built-in
OL,7, screens under proposed updates to the  
OL,8, Highway Code.                          
OL,10,FThe changes will say drivers must be   
OL,11,Fready to take back control of vehicles 
OL,12,Fwhen prompted, the government said.    
OL,14,FThe first use of self-driving          
OL,15,Ftechnology is likely to be when        
OL,16,Ftravelling at slow speeds on motorways,
OL,17,Fsuch as in congested traffic.          
OL,19,FHowever, using mobile phones while     
OL,20,Fdriving will remain illegal.           
